{
  "name": "Leaf Kick",
  "type": "spell",
  "img": "systems/n5eb/assets/Icons%20%26%20Images/Icons/Taijutsu.png",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You deliver a single falling kick, strong enough to bring the environment crumbling down around you. Make a Melee Taijutsu attack against a creature within range. On a hit you deal your Unarmed damage + 1d12 and the target must make a Strength saving throw. On a failed save they gain 1 rank of Slowed until the end of their next turn.</p><p>If this jutsu is used as a Finisher, you instead deal your [Unarmed Damage] + 3d12 and on a failed save the target falls prone as your force them into the ground shattering it, causing the area within a 10ft cube originating from you to be treated as difficult terrain.</p><p>At Higher Ranks: For each rank you cast this jutsu above D-Rank, increase the cost of this jutsu by 3 and damage by 1d12.</p>",
      "chat": ""
    },
